{"tid":279352,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1702號熱帶氣旋 苗柏MERBOK(04W)","createTime":"2017-06-11T08:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T05:37:18.000Z","uid":48733,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03e3c10a640f507608706d5c89bbe1983eac83d3","tid":279352,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"【颱風追擊】1702號熱帶氣旋 苗柏MERBOK(04W)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">[IMG]//<a href=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png[/IMG]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png%5B%2FIMG%5D&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0c8affa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">imgur.com/Pskei0w.png[/IMG]</a> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋苗柏</ins></span></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1702號熱帶氣旋 苗柏 MERBOK(04W)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：馬來西亞<br />\r\n意義：頸部有斑點的鴿子，常見於郊外和荒地，是馬來西亞人喜愛飼養的一種雀鳥。</span></span></strong><br />\r\n <br />\r\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n[img]//<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1706.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fnwp_1706.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0e4e5145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1706.png[/img]</a> [img]//<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1706.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Ftc_1706.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0f004b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">w