 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勿演交易消息"},{"pid":"c1aae24ecdd686496eb7654eaeea9cfef382c5d3","tid":279352,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"太廢了，升唔到級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ccc31020b779d42d42bb8722b0456856adad70","tid":279352,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>【颱風追擊】1702號熱帶氣旋 苗柏MERBOK(04W)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋苗柏</ins></span></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1702號熱帶氣旋 苗柏 MERBOK(04W)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：馬來西亞<br />\r\n意義：頸部有斑點的鴿子，常見於郊外和荒地，是馬來西亞人喜愛飼養的一種雀鳥。</span></span></strong><br />\r\n <br />\r\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1707.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fnwp_1707.png&h=a53ada5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1707.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Ftc_1707.png&h=a10f909c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 香港天文台 (HKO)<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1702-00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph%2Fimages%2Fzooml%2F1702-00.png&h=14a57bfa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1702-00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph%2Fimages%2Fzoom5l%2F1702-00.png&h=6f5f258a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA)<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://metoc.ndbc.noaa.gov/ProductFeeds-portlet/img/jtwc/products/wp0417.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetoc.ndbc.noaa.gov%2FProductFeeds-portlet%2Fimg%2Fjtwc%2Fproducts%2Fwp0417.gif&h=59b3324b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201704W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tropicalstormrisk.com%2Ftracker%2Fdynamic%2Fimages%2F201704W.png&h=3144656c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC)<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://icons.wunderground.com/data/images/wp201704_model.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficons.wunderground.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2Fwp201704_model.gif&h=56e403ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://icons-ak.wunderground.com/data/images/wp201704_ensmodel.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficons-ak.wunderground.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2Fwp201704_ensmodel.gif&h=2f18a075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 全球預報系統 (GFS)<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/MERBOK.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftyphoon2000.ph%2Fmulti%2Fdata%2FMERBOK.PNG&h=b4638d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 各機構綜合預測<br />\r\n <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://tropic.ssec.wisc.edu/real-time/mimic-tc/2017_04W/webManager/last48hrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftropic.ssec.wisc.edu%2Freal-time%2Fmimic-tc%2F2017_04W%2FwebManager%2Flast48hrs.gif&h=57f32475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n▲ 過去48小時動畫</strong>"},{"pid":"dd608d665e1789fab3b8ad023ab050ed831cea45","tid":279352,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:22:49.000